<div class='vspace'></div><h5>ihler  &mdash; </h5>
<div class='messageitem' > 
<p>Feel free to add (anonymous or signed) comments, questions, or other discussion items about the class, including lecture, homework, etc.  Please remain polite.  I reserve the right to moderate and remove posts.  Posts must be made from UCI machines.  For anonymous posts, just use any name (like, "anonymous").
</p></div>
